title: Auto exports decline 21% in 2023: SIAM
description: Overall exports stood at 42,85,809 units last year compared to 52,04,966 units in 2022. Passenger vehicle shipments rose 5% to 6,77,956 units last year from 6,44,842 units in 2022.
